# F16 admin — environment template.
# Vite only exposes vars prefixed with VITE_ to the client bundle.
# Copy to .env.local for local dev; never commit .env files.

# Note: the admin frontend talks to the backend via relative URLs (`/v1/...`,
# `/ws`) and relies on the Vite dev proxy (vite.config.ts -> server.proxy) in
# dev and on the reverse proxy / same-origin deploy in prod. As a result there
# is intentionally NO VITE_API_BASE_URL / VITE_WS_URL here. If you ever need to
# point the admin at a non-local backend, add an explicit override variable.
